#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"- Make Git verify the integrity of transferred objects. ([[!tails_ticket "
"11107]])"
msgstr ""
"- Git verifiziert nun die Integrität übertragener Objekte. ([[!tails_ticket "
"11107]])"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"For more details, see also our [changelog](https://git-tails.immerda.ch/"
